      @dsmoothInv_sInf _ _ _ fun d hd ↦ @DiffeologicalGroup.toDSmoothInv G d _ <| h d hd
    toDSmoothMul :=
      @dsmoothMul_sInf _ _ _ fun d hd ↦ @DiffeologicalGroup.toDSmoothMul G d _ <| h d hd }
```

This proves that the infimum of a set of diffeological groups is also a diffeological group. This is a standard result in the theory of diffeologies.

